Params: {3: "With Liv's help, you finally put on this slightly bulky equipment."}
{2: 'I feel a little stuffy.', 3: '7', 4: "It's quite warm inside.", 5: '9'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Too bad my thruster can only blow cold air...', 4: '1'}
{3: 'You probably have spent too much time putting on the suit. When you look down, the bonfire only has cinders left and could go out anytime.'}
{3: 'You want to ask what that means, but the bell has rung from afar.'}
{3: 'The bonfire finally goes out. It is completely dark.'}
